text:
Sense Health | Backend Engineer | Rotterdam, Netherlands | On Location (Relocation + Visa sponsorship possible)

https://www.sense-health.com/careers-2/senior-back-end-engin...

Sense Health is changing the mental health landscape of the Netherlands. We have partnered with the biggest mental health institute of the Netherlands to provide remote therapy using our service NiceDay (https://niceday.app/).

Come join me for the mental health revolution in the Netherlands and work with our cutting edge backend and DevOps team!
